reviews:
Great stop which was recommended by our son; going south on 1, if you get to Big Sur Deli on right, you are about 1/2 mile too far; we got directions at Deli but road is marked Narrow Road, no RV's,etc. about a 2 mile wiggle down a 1.5 lane road; worth it for sure, great beach and views; fix of people some for a break, some for the day; waves excellent for surfing;

Would definitely do this stop again
Show less
